episodes.title: #54: Misty Gilbert - Cult Survivor to Entrepreneur - Independence as a Survival Mechanism
episodes.description: -Misty W Gilbert was born and raised inside a cult located in Paso Robles, California, where she survived nightmarish abuse at the hands of her parents and religious community. Currently residing in Fort Worth, Texas, Misty is a three-business entrepreneur, Tedx alumni, transformational coach, blogger, writer, and speaker with a passion to encourage, support and inspire you to create the life that you want by choosing to intentionally live.
